<h1>About</h1>

<img src="/assets/about/biemmezeta.jpg" alt="Brunetto Marco Ziosi">

<p class="about-intro">
I’m Brunetto Marco Ziosi, a photographer based in Venice.
</p>

<p>
My work moves between portraits, weddings, music events and documentary photography,
always focusing on people and the stories they carry.
</p>

<p>
Before photography I worked in astrophysics and software engineering,
but eventually chose to dedicate myself fully to visual storytelling.
</p>

<p>
I collaborate with artists, couples, cultural organisations and events,
documenting moments, places and human connections.
</p>

